Responsibilities:

Assists in preparing policy and endorsements;
Assist in document sorting and filling, quality checking, policy binding;
Handling internal enquiry in daily inward business
To able to work independently and under pressure, detail-oriented and self-motivated;
To perform ad-hoc assignment as required;
